{"tha-ap15:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap15:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap15:0.3":"Nandattheraapadana ","tha-ap15:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap15:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap15:1.3":"Vattham khomam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap15:1.4":"Sayambhussa mahesino. ","tha-ap15:2.1":"Tam me buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap15:2.2":"jalajuttaranamako; ","tha-ap15:2.3":"‘Imina vatthadanena, ","tha-ap15:2.4":"hemavanno bhavissasi. ","tha-ap15:3.1":"Dve sampatti anubhotva, ","tha-ap15:3.2":"kusalamulehi codito; ","tha-ap15:3.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap15:3.4":"kanittho tvam bhavissasi. ","tha-ap15:4.1":"Ragaratto sukhasilo, ","tha-ap15:4.2":"kamesu gedhamayuto; ","tha-ap15:4.3":"Buddhena codito santo, ","tha-ap15:4.4":"tada tvam pabbajissasi. ","tha-ap15:5.1":"Pabbajitvana tvam tattha, ","tha-ap15:5.2":"kusalamulena codito; ","tha-ap15:5.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap15:5.4":"nibbayissasinasavo’. ","tha-ap15:6.1":"Satta kappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap15:6.2":"caturo celanamaka; ","tha-ap15:6.3":"Satthi kappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap15:6.4":"upacela catujjana. ","tha-ap15:7.1":"Panca kappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap15:7.2":"celava caturo jana; ","tha-ap15:7.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap15:7.4":"catudipamhi issara. ","tha-ap15:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap15:8.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap15:8.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap15:8.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap15:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nando thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap15:10.1":"Nandattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}